<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.9">
<l>aṅka malap pōta katti laṇikoḷ muttañ cinti ṉāṟpōṟ</l>
<l>ceṅka malamu kamvi yarppat tīmai ceytim muṟṟat tūṭē</l>
<l>yaṅka mellām puḻuti yāka vaḷaiya vēṇṭā vamma vimma</l>
<l>vaṅka marark kamuta ḷitta vamarar kōvē mulaiyuṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do not make mishchief such that your red lotus face sweats</l>
<l rend="indent">Like beautiful pearls scatterd inside a lovely lotus bud,</l>
<l>It’s unnecessary to wallow in this courtyard</l>
<l>so the all your limbs are [covered in] dust!</l>
<l>Alas! King of the celestials who at one time</l>
<l>granted nectar to the immortals so that they were full!</l>
<l rend="indent">Drink from [my] breast!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
